<h2 id="how-to-use-this-hot-swapping-guide">How to Use This Hot Swapping Guide</h2>

<p>Since I couldn‚Äôt find any traditional cases with a hot swap feature, I had to find hot swappable adapters and compatible cases.</p>

<p>Some adapters are meant for 3.5‚Äù drives, while others are meant for 2.5‚Äù drives.</p>

<p>That being said, I‚Äôve organized this guide in two parts:</p>

<ul>
  <li>3.5‚Äù hot swap drive cage</li>
  <li>2.5‚Äù hot swap drive cage</li>
</ul>

<p>Each section has a featured hot swap drive cage, along with a few cases that you can use.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> The hot swap drive cages can be used with any compatible case, but not all cases are compatible. That‚Äôs why I‚Äôve selected some cases for you already that are compatible.**</p>

<p>Hopefully this helps!</p>

